WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:01.267
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.596 --> 00:00:07.920
I'm going to do a video right now that's a little different than what I usually do.

00:00:09.582 --> 00:00:15.930
Everybody's been telling me about this earthquake and all the stuff that's going on in Italy.

00:00:16.480 --> 00:00:23.017
Back on July 5th, I did a video about a major volcano going off.

00:00:23.451 --> 00:00:34.093
The Lord warned me about this volcano back on July 5th and told me this would be very destructive, there would be a lot of damage, and a lot of people would pass away.

00:00:34.706 --> 00:00:37.600
I saw two or 300,000 people; it's massive.

00:00:38.391 --> 00:00:43.106
He showed me to focus on the ocean in this gulf right here.

00:00:43.106 --> 00:00:50.679
I saw there is a massive volcano out here somewhere.

00:00:50.1000 --> 00:00:56.611
I believed it was right in here, because Pompeii is right here.

00:00:56.611 --> 00:00:57.988
There's a massive volcano up here.

00:00:59.640 --> 00:01:06.594
When I was looking over in the spirit and it was showing me, I thought it was in this right here, but I believe it's probably further out.

00:01:07.176 --> 00:01:17.690
I started looking at where the massive volcanoes in the water over in Italy are.

00:01:17.690 --> 00:01:24.110
If you zoom out, I'll show you.

00:01:24.110 --> 00:01:31.566
There's a massive volcano—one of the largest—way down here.

00:01:31.566 --> 00:01:43.044
Whenever I saw this massive volcano going off out of the water, it caused a massive tsunami wave.

00:01:52.230 --> 00:02:05.335
It exploded from the earthquake and this massive volcano; it was like a humongous nuclear bomb went off and it went up out of the water and caused a massive wave that washed all inland.

00:02:05.335 --> 00:02:08.879
Can you go back out?

00:02:08.879 --> 00:02:15.658
Can you make the map where I can show the people?

00:02:15.658 --> 00:02:17.501
Go down.

00:02:17.501 --> 00:02:24.940
Okay, so the water rushed all over this area.

00:02:39.200 --> 00:02:39.571
It would cause a lot of devastation.

00:02:39.571 --> 00:03:03.351
One of these volcanoes out here, the Lord is showing me, it came up out of the water and it caused all the air traffic around that area to be completely shut down.

00:03:04.061 --> 00:03:20.468
The Lord showed me that it would cost hundreds of thousands of deaths when this happened, and he said one of the major signs to watch out for was earthquakes and tremors.

00:03:20.468 --> 00:03:28.205
He said back in July, I don't believe there were any tremors; there weren't any earthquakes.

00:03:33.959 --> 00:03:45.140
And then all of a sudden, here we see the article that says there was the biggest earthquake in 40 years that happened in that area that I'm talking about.

00:03:48.400 --> 00:03:51.239
It happened this week; it was a 4.

00:03:51.239 --> 00:03:52.079
2.

00:04:00.288 --> 00:04:06.147
Going on and reading even more, there's been hundreds of little bitty earthquakes that they've picked up around that area.

00:04:06.147 --> 00:04:27.620
So it's going with what the Lord showed me would happen back in July: to start praying and that it would be a serious event that would take place out in the water.

00:04:27.620 --> 00:04:33.662
He kept telling me to pray over the water.

00:04:33.662 --> 00:04:51.600
If you start to see some kind of smoke coming up out of the water, that's probably hundreds of miles off the coast.

00:04:51.600 --> 00:05:06.947
If you start hearing stuff about the ocean, this is a very high alert for you all if you're already having these earthquakes.

00:05:08.280 --> 00:05:16.120
The Lord warned me about this clear back in July.

00:05:25.285 --> 00:05:43.253
I don't know if this is what we're looking for, or if the volcano is about to happen imminently, but it was very strong in my spirit in July and I've been interceding for this.

00:05:43.253 --> 00:05:51.543
Now I'm going to go to the next thing.

00:05:51.543 --> 00:05:58.948
Like I told you all, I was interceding for the elections for 2024.

00:06:02.493 --> 00:06:12.120
I saw Michelle Obama and I saw Gavin, and nothing was in the news back when this was going on.

00:06:12.120 --> 00:06:14.776
This was this time last year.

00:06:14.776 --> 00:06:31.919
Getting closer to the fall, I really believe we're about to see some kind of major shakeup in the Democratic Party in the near future.

00:06:31.919 --> 00:06:40.210
Sarah Palin is already saying that she believes Michelle Obama will be the Democratic nominee in 2024.

00:06:40.210 --> 00:06:51.346
Then we have Ted Cruz, who says that he believes that Michelle Obama could be the 2024 candidate too.

00:06:53.800 --> 00:07:04.229
What I saw in the supernatural is starting to happen; people in political positions in the know are starting to echo it.

00:07:11.180 --> 00:07:17.268
I saw another article on 60 Minutes with Gavin not denying that he wanted to maybe run for president.

00:07:17.268 --> 00:07:30.525
In the vision that the Lord showed me, he was the vice president and Michelle Obama was the president.

00:07:30.525 --> 00:07:43.994
Joe Biden was not able to keep going because of his mental problems; I believe it's dementia or something.

00:07:45.439 --> 00:07:49.546
The Lord was warning me about this.

00:08:06.771 --> 00:08:07.167
I saw him being pulled out, not even finishing.

00:08:07.167 --> 00:08:10.053
Kamala Harris would start running things.

00:08:10.053 --> 00:08:28.766
I saw a woman whose face was shaded out; it was blurry in the vision and I could not see it, but I could see her hair.

00:08:28.766 --> 00:08:38.965
It was a blonde woman and her hair was a shorter haircut.

00:08:38.965 --> 00:08:49.662
I believe the way the hair looked, it was either Elizabeth Warren or it could be Hillary Clinton.

00:08:49.662 --> 00:08:53.080
Now, these are just my assumptions.

00:08:53.080 --> 00:09:10.213
Whether or not this vision comes to pass, I don't know, but it's something that I've been praying over for over a year now.

00:09:10.213 --> 00:09:17.453
We prophesy in part, we hear in part, and we see in part.

00:09:17.453 --> 00:09:35.907
We're seeing this stuff come up in the news now: the earthquakes, the political stuff, and the Lord's warning about the Prince of Saudi Arabia and the price of oil.

00:09:35.907 --> 00:09:55.886
Remember what I told you all about that going over $200 a barrel and him making a secret agreement with Russia and with China and joining the BRICS nations?

00:09:55.886 --> 00:10:00.760
We saw that happen on August 24th.

00:10:00.760 --> 00:10:07.375
They want to join up with them on January 1st.

00:10:10.119 --> 00:10:15.394
All those major places—Venezuela, Egypt, the UAE—and he even warned me about Iraq.

00:10:15.394 --> 00:10:22.480
Here is JP Morgan saying $150 a barrel of oil.

00:10:22.480 --> 00:10:30.370
They're forecasting $150, and that's just in the beginning stages.

00:10:30.370 --> 00:10:46.280
We're so close to that vision and what the Lord warned me about gas prices going over $7 or $8 a gallon.

00:10:55.907 --> 00:10:56.160
In California, they're already charging that.

00:11:00.420 --> 00:11:00.830
I believe a nationwide average is coming.

00:11:07.420 --> 00:11:07.630
We are in the end times.

00:11:07.630 --> 00:11:10.560
Jesus Christ is coming back.

00:11:10.560 --> 00:11:16.817
We are in the last of the last days.

00:11:16.817 --> 00:11:27.989
When we start seeing earthquakes, volcanoes go off, and political upheaval, we're seeing all these birthing pains.

00:11:27.989 --> 00:11:51.346
I believe it was the video I did just a couple days ago; the Lord was showing me from Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah, this is going to be an acceleration of birthing pains.

00:11:51.346 --> 00:11:59.446
You're going to see an acceleration in the weather, the political area, and in war.

00:11:59.446 --> 00:12:10.270
I remember I tried to tell you all about a major draft coming for the United States of America.

00:12:10.270 --> 00:12:28.912
I've been praying against this because the Lord showed me men and women being drafted and going into Ukraine, with this war escalating with Russia.

00:12:31.298 --> 00:12:37.089
I saw Russia going after Poland and bombing Poland with some kind of super bomb.

00:12:37.089 --> 00:12:41.040
It was around the Warsaw and Belarus area.

00:12:56.620 --> 00:12:56.970
I saw Joe Biden telling everybody that we wanted to lend them $2 billion to help out with their military.

00:12:56.970 --> 00:13:10.205
So there is stuff that I saw over a year ago starting to manifest in the news.

00:13:16.860 --> 00:13:17.110
People wanted to know about the New Madrid Fault.

00:13:22.368 --> 00:13:28.010
The Lord warned me that if we divide Jerusalem, he would divide the land, which would cause a curse on America.

00:13:40.350 --> 00:13:40.621
If you come against Israel, it's like we're betraying her because we've been in covenant with her.

00:13:40.621 --> 00:14:04.445
I believe with all my heart, three days after they divide the land of Israel, we will see one of the greatest earthquakes we've ever had in America on the New Madrid Fault going up America.

00:14:04.445 --> 00:14:06.560
I've seen it.

00:14:06.560 --> 00:14:15.486
Earthquakes go from there because they cause a chain reaction over the area.

00:14:15.486 --> 00:14:23.777
It's not just about that earthquake; it sets off other fault lines all throughout America.

00:14:23.777 --> 00:14:27.289
When a major earthquake—like a 10.

00:14:27.289 --> 00:14:33.108
0, a massive earthquake—hits, it destroys all the bridges.

00:14:33.108 --> 00:14:37.020
I warned you all about that.

00:14:37.020 --> 00:14:40.440
So here we are.

00:14:40.440 --> 00:14:59.199
The Prince of Saudi Arabia comes on the news saying he wants a two-state solution to help so they can build the Third Temple.

00:14:59.199 --> 00:15:04.480
They have a peace agreement and all the stuff they want to do.

00:15:04.480 --> 00:15:10.314
And when do they want to have it done?

00:15:10.314 --> 00:15:24.639
I've already talked about this before; they want to have that done before the big solar eclipse that goes across America.

00:15:24.639 --> 00:15:28.690
We are so close to major events domino-effecting.

00:15:34.128 --> 00:15:36.180
I warned you all about the dollar crash and to watch Europe.

00:15:36.180 --> 00:15:41.514
He told me to watch the Euro; it's a very significant domino.

00:15:45.080 --> 00:15:50.999
I saw something someone sent me on Facebook about how the Euro and the European currency were in trouble.

00:15:50.999 --> 00:15:56.583
It's all being accelerated just like the Lord told me.

00:15:56.583 --> 00:15:59.625
We are so close to a major event happening.

00:15:59.625 --> 00:16:10.533
I've warned you how the Lord has me pray about the pulses in the spirit, and I feel very strongly about the month of October.

00:16:10.533 --> 00:16:19.543
We have a major event coming on October 4th with this FEMA alert on our phones.

00:16:19.543 --> 00:16:38.720
People are freaking out about that, and then we have Russia now saying they're going to do some kind of event on the third regarding nuclear stuff.

00:16:38.720 --> 00:16:44.552
The whole world is stirring right now.

00:16:44.552 --> 00:16:54.509
It's a time to be prayed up and get in the Word even more.

00:16:54.509 --> 00:17:03.343
If you hear the Spirit of God telling you to do something, obey Him.

00:17:10.199 --> 00:17:11.319
If He tells you to relocate, follow the voice of the Lord.

00:17:11.319 --> 00:17:21.744
It should be your heart's cry every day: 'Father, what do You have for my family today?

00:17:21.744 --> 00:17:24.284
Lead and guide me.

00:17:24.284 --> 00:17:27.226
I'm desperate for more of You, to hear Your voice, and for a relationship with You.

00:17:27.226 --> 00:17:34.970
' You need to be sitting at the feet of Jesus daily, not just on Sunday.

00:17:34.970 --> 00:17:40.371
I might have messed up my wording, my verbiage.

00:17:40.371 --> 00:17:46.320
What I'm trying to tell you is that you need to seek Him every day.

00:17:53.720 --> 00:17:55.138
Have a relationship with Jesus Monday through Sunday, all the time, sitting at His feet.

00:17:55.138 --> 00:17:58.600
In Him, He'll have all the things laid out for you.

00:17:58.600 --> 00:18:01.940
In Him, there's peace, joy, and longsuffering.

00:18:01.940 --> 00:18:21.846
There's provision when you're seeking the face of God and not just His hand—always looking for just the provision like a child asking, 'God, what do You have in Your hand for me today?

00:18:21.846 --> 00:18:26.743
' No, Father, Abba, Abba Father, I want You today.

00:18:30.129 --> 00:18:30.537
I want a relationship with You.

00:18:32.033 --> 00:18:37.960
It's about growing up and coming up higher spiritually.

00:18:42.060 --> 00:18:46.754
It's time for another level in our walk with Jesus instead of just coming to Him with our needs.

00:18:55.909 --> 00:19:00.209
Not that that's wrong, but it should be more than that; it's about being intimate with Him.

00:19:09.929 --> 00:19:16.760
If I only came to my wife and asked her to do the laundry and cook dinner without any other relationship, it would be very bad.

00:19:16.760 --> 00:19:29.783
Having a relationship is more than just always coming to God with a need; it's having fellowship with Him and worshiping Him.

00:19:40.360 --> 00:19:40.680
The Bible says that if we don't praise Him, the rocks will cry out.

00:19:40.680 --> 00:19:46.988
I'm not going to let a rock do my job.

00:19:46.988 --> 00:19:52.320
Sit at His feet daily, worship Him, sing songs, and practice His presence.

00:19:52.320 --> 00:20:07.360
If you start asking Him what's on His heart every single day, He's going to start pouring Himself into you.

00:20:07.360 --> 00:20:12.164
It's a conversation, just like you have with your spouse.

00:20:14.332 --> 00:20:15.940
You talk because you love that person.

00:20:19.782 --> 00:20:21.1000
That's the kind of relationship you should have with the Lord.

00:20:28.635 --> 00:20:29.871
I want a God I can talk to and be real with.

00:20:30.053 --> 00:20:35.240
I don't get religious and weird; I just get real.

00:20:35.240 --> 00:20:38.331
'Hey God, I love You.

00:20:38.331 --> 00:20:47.834
' I even talk to Him about basketball; He loves NBA basketball.

00:20:47.834 --> 00:20:51.232
He watches it with me.

00:20:51.232 --> 00:20:55.166
It's being personable with God.

00:20:55.166 --> 00:21:13.505
Abraham had a friendship with Him; He can visit Brandon, Bobby, or whoever is on the other end of this camera.

00:21:14.560 --> 00:21:29.540
I believe with all my heart God has a plan for your life and wants to warn you about what's coming.

00:21:29.540 --> 00:21:33.669
He's no respecter of persons.

00:21:33.669 --> 00:21:39.133
I want to pray for you right now.

00:21:39.133 --> 00:21:46.062
There's no fear here; perfect love casteth out all fear.

00:21:46.062 --> 00:21:46.613
God's got us.

00:21:46.613 --> 00:21:54.505
He said He's never seen the righteous forsaken nor his seed begging bread.

00:21:54.505 --> 00:22:00.664
If He takes care of the lilies of the field and the birds of the air, He's going to take care of you.

00:22:00.664 --> 00:22:12.159
Father, I thank You that every need is met in the name of Jesus—over their bodies, minds, and emotions.

00:22:14.578 --> 00:22:21.360
I take authority over the demonic spirits of fear, depression, anxiety, and worry.

00:22:23.570 --> 00:22:25.815
I command healing to flow over them.

00:22:25.815 --> 00:22:28.240
I see PTSD right now.

00:22:40.010 --> 00:22:40.320
I take authority over post-traumatic stress disorder and cast you out.

00:22:40.320 --> 00:22:47.750
I command freedom in their thoughts and healing over their brain waves.

00:23:00.213 --> 00:23:00.620
We cast those reoccurring traumatic thoughts down.

00:23:00.620 --> 00:23:14.805
2 Timothy 1:7 says God has not given us a spirit of fear but of power, love, and a sound mind.

00:23:16.560 --> 00:23:21.060
I call your mind balanced right now.

00:23:27.960 --> 00:23:29.380
I bind the strongman and command you to be set free.

00:23:29.380 --> 00:23:33.240
No more PTSD or suicidal thoughts.

00:23:40.120 --> 00:23:40.440
We plead the blood of Jesus over your mind.

00:23:40.760 --> 00:24:01.931
Father, I thank You that our sisters and brothers are healed from the top of their heads to the soles of their feet from diabetes, heart disease, lupus, glaucoma, or whatever it may be.

00:24:03.320 --> 00:24:10.280
We speak to stomach issues, liver problems, and the colon—from diverticulitis to Crohn's disease.

00:24:27.046 --> 00:24:27.314
I curse autoimmune disease and call thyroids to line up and be healed.

00:24:27.314 --> 00:24:30.815
I call leukemia healed in Jesus' name.

00:24:37.663 --> 00:24:45.073
You said in Your Word that whatsoever things we desire when we pray, believe that we receive them and we shall have them.

00:24:51.919 --> 00:24:55.180
And if we shall not doubt in our heart, we shall have whatsoever things we say.

00:24:57.200 --> 00:24:58.400
I thank You for Mark 11:24.

00:24:58.400 --> 00:25:04.090
Faith calls those things to be not as though they were.

00:25:11.600 --> 00:25:11.800
I call you healed, well, and delivered.

00:25:11.800 --> 00:25:18.499
We call in finances—new jobs, raises, bonuses, and inheritances.

00:25:18.499 --> 00:25:27.455
I thank You, Lord, that You're meeting all their financial needs.

00:25:27.455 --> 00:25:32.809
Every seed you sow will reap a hundredfold.

00:25:42.796 --> 00:25:45.475
I thank You, Lord, that they have good ground, and it would be just like miracle ground and spring forth a mighty harvest.

00:25:53.240 --> 00:25:54.200
Thank you for joining us today.

00:25:54.200 --> 00:25:59.905
Comment below about the volcanoes if you know more about that area.

00:25:59.905 --> 00:26:01.620
I pray a hedge of protection over you.

00:26:01.620 --> 00:26:04.640
Don't be afraid, but if the Lord tells you to get out in the middle of the night, flee fast.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
Put a smile on your face; Jesus loves you.
